title: -=Xploitz=- Master Password List LITE
description:
I downloaded -=Xploitz=- 3.5 gig master password list combined all lists then sorted in alphabetical order and deleted duplicates.This took almost 3 hours on my old server so I thought I would save others time and put the streamlined list out on the Tubes. This list is a single text file that unpacks to a brisk 1 gig and from what i can tell the most comprehensive text file for password testing out there. 

Enjoy and don't use this for anything naughty
